Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H2B2883&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist's Final All-Out Attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is GOD's secret base in\NJapan: the Palace of Apollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist spends three hours\Na day on its shooting range...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...Training for the sole purpose\Nof defeating the X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Guard captain, show me my\Nresults for the past week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It started three days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I normally score\Nthree bull's eyes, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One miss... Two misses...\NAnd three misses today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong\Nwith my trigger finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your coffee, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you another sir,\Nit won't take a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me sir, but\Nis something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't... look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't I the immortal Apollo\NGeist, the pride of GOD!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Supreme Commander revived\Nme an immortal body, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Hayata and Dr. Miyamoto\Nwho performed the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\i1}Miyamoto{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You oversaw my resuscitation.\NYou must know what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your body malfunctioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,For three days now... my\Nfingers have been seizing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Paralysis of the fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... It's started at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What has started!?\NExplain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you're hurting me! Let me go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what's wrong\Nwith me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The operation was only able\Nto extend your life for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll start with finger paralysis, and\Nthen you'll lose control of your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end... your brain\Nwill cease to function.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do I have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If the finger paralysis\Nbegan three days ago, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Today at the earliest,\Ntomorrow at the latest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You revived me once. You'll do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Replace my defective organs with new ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't, it's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you killed Hayata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do another operation\Nlike that without Hayata's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayata... Forget about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can at least replace\Nmy mechanical parts alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible either, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider may be able to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The X Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Specifically... the X Rider's Perfecter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider's Perfecter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Attaching the Perfecter\Nto your heart might solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I've more reason than\Never to kill the X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My thanks, Dr. Miyamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your role is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Today at the earliest,\Ntomorrow at the latest...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill the X Rider and\Ntake the Perfecter first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sneak up on\Na guy like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There something I\Ncan do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Miyamoto!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We met in the Palace of Apollon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's with GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke-- No, X Rider!\NDo you recognise my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Apollo Geist's\Nfinal challenge to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You will settle things at the\NPalace of Apollon's fighting arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you aren't there in twelve hours,\Nthose two lovely ladies you know will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No! He's got Chiko and Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, Apollo Geist is\Nlooking forward to seeing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD, those cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, maybe Chiko\Nand Mako are still--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they haven't got them yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all up to you, Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiko! Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Snap out of it! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a little\Ntoo late, Jin Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the GOD commander's dolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist is a man of his word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Be at the Palace of\NApollon within twelve hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Apollo Geist! I don't know\Nwhere the Palace of Apollon is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I will provide a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't assume you'll\Nmake it there alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the way to\Nthe Palace of Apollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But what Apollo Geist said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,'Don't assume you'll\Nmake it there alive'...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised, Jin Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed us once, but Apollo\NGeist has relit our flames of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time we won't fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke... You won't make it to\Nthe Palace of Apollon alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...Because we're going\Nto kill you here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Having fun, Jin Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Kawakami's name was changed to Dr. Hayata\Nin this ep, so we've implied Hayata's his first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Electro Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Crown Splitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist wasn't bluffing,\Nchief. They've got them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's this guy gonna\Ndo about wrecking my shop!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't blame you for being angry, but\Nbe patient. He still has his uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What use could he possibly be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll give us the edge on Apollo Geist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fool yourselves! You\Nthink Achilles would talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles! You should make the\Nmost of this second chance at life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the X Rider's right. Even\Na GOD monster wants to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you'd spare me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:14:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might've been getting\Ntired of taking Apollo Geist's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No kidding! Alright, I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn that GOD... I should send\Nthem a compensation claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you asked, I think that\Nshould cover the refurbishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is for Jin Keisuke's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want an enemy thinking ill of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that! Let the girls go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's how you want it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't give the game away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who's there?\N-It's me, Achilles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Apollo Geist\NI've got Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Achilles for you... The\Nelevator will be right down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it snappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, Achilles. Apollo\NGeist will be pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-This way, you--\N-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take him to Apollo Geist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir. Allow us to escort you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist, Achilles has\Nbrought Jin Keisuke here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? Why was Achilles\Nholding the Perfecter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want with the Perfecter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, it was Achilles who\Ncaught Jin Keisuke--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad little trick, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But not good enough to fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You always were a smart one, Apollo Geist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Someone save us!\N-Chiko! Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Help!\N-Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiko? Mako?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:17:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keisuke!\N-Save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-A tape...\N-You'll have to settle for us instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna enjoy this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Hammer Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Apollo Geist? Don't you\Nwant to fight me? Where are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:19:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Our final duel at last...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All of those useless fools are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you fight with all you have!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I have to know...\NWhere are your hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-X Rider!\N-Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta win! Justice always wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! There's a third!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me, just save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to die, I'll oblige you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Cruiser! Save the chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the girls, chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Boss!\N-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Geist Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Magnum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Apollo Geist? You're\Nnot the marksman you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...Listen, X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I will die soon. I can't\Nchange my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't die alone. You're\Ncoming to hell with me, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, GOD!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like this really is\Nthe end of Apollo Geist...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Palace of Apollon will follow him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is King Dark! You\Nand I will fight someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider has vanquished\NApollo Geist at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But just who is the mysterious King Dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider is dogged by a\Nstrange feeling uneasiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(45,10)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider has destroyed Apollo\NGeist and the Palace of Apollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But a terrifying new plan is\Nalready brewing in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.90,0:23:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind it is King Dark. Just\Nwhat kind of being is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.10,0:23:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Terrifying Giant! King Dark Emerges!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider